And no, i do not mean the champion.

I remember everyone saying 

&quot;support is the easiest role, i dont see how you can do bad in it!&quot; 

&quot;your such a failure at league. Your playing support and cant even play that!&quot; 

&quot;support mains are trash at league, they cant even play anything else!&quot;

Autofill comes.

&quot;OH GOD I AM AUTOFILLED SUPPORT!&quot;

&quot;CAN I PLEASE GET A DIFFERENT ROLE? ANYTHING BUT SUPPORT, I CANT SUPPORT!&quot;

Im so glad for autofill, because all the other support mains just rub our hands together and go

&quot;MUHAHAHAHAHA the time of reconing has come. Let the battles begin.&quot;

